data.description: One level living at its very best. Well maintained 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Brick Ranch style home situated on a level .55 acre  lot.  Roof, plumbing, hot water heater, new stainless steel appliances, all less than 3 years old. A storage building which is perfect for storing your lawn equipment. This home is conveniently located to everything, shopping, grocery stores, restaurants, hospital. Call today for your private showing.
